// LAE Waybar modules — installed via `lae install waybar`
// Replaces hyprland/workspaces with task-scoped desktop indicators.
//
// Modules:
//   custom/lae-task       — current task name (click: task menu, right-click: default)
//   custom/lae-desktop-1  — desktop 1 within current context (SUPER+1 equivalent)
//   custom/lae-desktop-2  — desktop 2
//   custom/lae-desktop-3  — desktop 3
